name: GemFind
overview:
Founded in 1999, GemFind is a privately held, Los Angeles-based business that has evolved the B2B wholesale diamond jewelry and gemstone marketplace by becoming the premier Internet destination for the entire jewelry industry.

The GemFind Network and website not only connect wholesale gemstone and wholesale diamond jewelry dealers from all over the world, it gives them access to a comprehensive set of online sales and marketing services aimed at reducing their overhead costs while increasing each members exposure and market-share in the competitive global marketplace.

Two of the most notable services GemFind offers its gemstone and wholesale diamond jewelry dealers are the GF Search tool and GF Index. GF Search is an online search tool that allows members to search through thousands of certified loose diamonds listed in the GemFind Database. The detailed search criteria, which include shape, size, clarity, cut, weight, depth, certificate type and price, allow diamond wholesalers to find diamonds matching their exact specifications.

GF Index is a proprietary online diamond appraisal system that is the most accurate in the world. By entering a diamonds defining characteristics into this online tool, it will immediately calculate an accurate, wholesale diamond appraisal.
